</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"widget subscribe"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;ul</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"social"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;li&gt;&lt;a</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">"http://feeds.feedburner.com/devgrow"</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"rss"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>RSS<span class="nt">&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;li&gt;&lt;a</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">"http://www.facebook.com/DevGrow"</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"facebook"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>Facebook<span class="nt">&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;li&gt;&lt;a</span> <span class="na">href=</span><span class="s">"http://twitter.com/ThinkDevGrow"</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"twitter"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>Twitter<span class="nt">&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;/ul&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;h3&gt;</span>Subscribe<span class="nt">&lt;/h3&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>Join over 2,800 readers and get the latest posts delivered straight to your inbox.<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;form</span> <span class="na">id=</span><span class="s">"feedburner-subscribe"</span> <span class="na">action=</span><span class="s">"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify"</span> <span class="na">method=</span><span class="s">"post"</span> <span class="na">target=</span><span class="s">"popupwindow"</span> <span class="na">onsubmit=</span><span class="s">"window.open('http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=[YourAccount]', 'popupwindow', 'scrollbars=yes,width=550,height=520');return true"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;input</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">"text"</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"email"</span> <span class="na">value=</span><span class="s">"E-mail Address"</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"left textfield"</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;input</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">"hidden"</span> <span class="na">value=</span><span class="s">"[YourAccount]"</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"uri"</span><span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;input</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">"hidden"</span> <span class="na">name=</span><span class="s">"loc"</span> <span class="na">value=</span><span class="s">"en_US"</span><span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
        <span class="nt">&lt;input</span> <span class="na">type=</span><span class="s">"submit"</span> <span class="na">value=</span><span class="s">"Subscribe"</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"right button submit"</span> <span class="nt">/&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;/form&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></figure>

<p>The HTML is pretty straightforward, the only thing out of the norm is the <a href="http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/emailsyndication">Feedburner e-mail widget</a>, which is taken directly from their site.  You can use any service there instead of Feedburner, or use a separate WordPress plugin to handle your subscriptions if you choose.</p>

